40:33.083 --> 40:35.208
taking the 15-minute taxi ride
back,

40:35.208 --> 40:36.792
I'm gonna make the guests
wait forever.

40:36.792 --> 40:37.917
Or...

40:40.083 --> 40:41.583
Hey, Captain, this is Kelley.

40:52.833 --> 40:53.417
- Is this Captain Lee?

40:53.292 --> 40:53.417
- Yeah.

40:54.708 --> 40:56.292
- Hey, Captain, this is Kelley.

40:56.292 --> 40:58.375
We have a mishap.

40:58.375 --> 41:01.417
We changed coolers
right as we switched--

41:01.417 --> 41:02.792
me and Nico...
- Yeah?

41:02.792 --> 41:04.958
- And he has the keys
to the "Intrepid."

41:04.958 --> 41:07.083
- So you have no way
to get out here.

41:07.083 --> 41:10.000
- No.
- So, you're sitting there,

41:10.000 --> 41:11.125
the guests are sitting there,

41:11.125 --> 41:13.458
and you're calling me.

41:13.458 --> 41:15.917
You just really screwed up.

41:15.917 --> 41:17.583
- I was thinking the RIB
could be put in.

41:17.583 --> 41:19.333
The RIB to the guests,
pick up the guests,

41:19.333 --> 41:21.792
bring them back to the boat,
and then come pick me up.

41:21.792 --> 41:23.292
Well, drop the keys off to me.

41:25.000 --> 41:28.292
- All right, I'll go
pick up Nico at the beach.

41:28.292 --> 41:30.500
So now I have to bail
your ass out,

41:30.500 --> 41:33.167
not because I particularly want
to bail your ass out,

41:33.167 --> 41:37.000
but the guests
need to be bailed out.

41:37.000 --> 41:39.792
I'll work it out,
and I will get back to you.

41:39.792 --> 41:41.333
- All right, thank you, Captain.
- Bye.

41:41.333 --> 41:42.458
- Bye.

41:43.833 --> 41:45.458
- Never a dull moment.

41:47.667 --> 41:50.042
- Where is he?

41:50.042 --> 41:52.500
- I know my ass is
about to be handed to me.

41:52.500 --> 41:55.542
And it might be
for the last time.

41:55.542 --> 41:57.042
- All right,
let's get the RIB in.

41:57.042 --> 41:58.542
Dean's probably
been sitting there,

41:58.542 --> 42:00.625
I don't know how long,
waiting for Kelley.

42:00.625 --> 42:03.000
- Why didn't Kelley leave the
"Intrepid" and go get the keys,

42:03.000 --> 42:04.875
and then go back
in all this time?

42:04.875 --> 42:07.208
- It's quicker to do this.
- Oh, man.

42:07.208 --> 42:08.667
This is a huge mistake.

42:08.667 --> 42:12.875
Especially with Dean.
This is just stupid.

42:12.875 --> 42:14.542
- Do what you can,
and I'll be back.

42:14.542 --> 42:16.833
Everything that could go wrong
is going wrong.

42:16.833 --> 42:18.542
This is a big bad.

42:18.542 --> 42:20.292
We've got charter guests
stuck on a beach

42:20.292 --> 42:22.375
with no way of getting them
off the beach.

42:22.375 --> 42:25.542
I'm terribly disappointed
and pissed.

42:25.542 --> 42:26.792
All of the above.

42:33.917 --> 42:35.250
- Next on "Below Deck"...

42:35.250 --> 42:37.250
- Ashley's on a plane
to Tortola.

42:37.250 --> 42:38.500
- Oh!

42:42.417 --> 42:43.500
- Right.

42:45.208 --> 42:46.917
- Did you have a nice time?

42:46.917 --> 42:49.417
- Kelley and Nico left us
stranded on a beach,

42:49.417 --> 42:52.000
so good times.
- Dean is pissed.

42:52.000 --> 42:56.500
- What I'd like to do is
rip your f---ing head off.

42:56.500 --> 42:58.000
- I'm trying to serve
the guests,

42:58.000 --> 42:59.583
because we're on charter,

42:59.583 --> 43:02.667
but those flowers--
- I want Emily to enjoy them.

43:02.667 --> 43:05.583
- I feel like I'm very much
caught in the middle.

43:05.583 --> 43:08.250
- We had a really nice thing
going on, and--

43:08.250 --> 43:10.042
- And why do we not still?
- I mean, do we?

43:10.042 --> 43:11.417
I don't know.

